@startuml
[*] --> Start :
Start --> GreetUser : The system shall greet the user when they arrive.
GreetUser --> InsertCard :
InsertCard --> CheckPIN : The system shall check the PIN after the card is inserted.
CheckPIN --> IncorrectPIN : The system shall allow the user to try again if the entered PIN is incorrect.
IncorrectPIN --> KeepCardForSecurity : The system shall keep the card for security if it is invalid or the PIN is entered incorrectly too many times.
KeepCardForSecurity --> ReturnCard : The system shall return the card if the user cancels the operation.
ReturnCard --> DisplayOptions : The system shall display available options (withdrawing money, checking information, or making a transfer) for the user to choose from if the PIN is correct.
DisplayOptions --> ProcessRequest : The system shall process the selected request after the user makes a choice.
ProcessRequest --> End :
@enduml
